<Abstract ID="Abs1" Language="En">
<Heading>Abstract</Heading>
<Para>In this chapter, I’ll cover the topic of personalization. I’ll begin with an introduction, examine personalization and the “long tail,” and review some sites that do personalization well today. I’ll also discuss how the claims on an information card could allow you to do personalization beginning with a consumer’s first visit and continuing throughout the life cycle.</Para>
</Abstract>
